%description
KMediaPlayer builds on the KParts framework to provide a common
interface for KParts that can play media files.

This framework is a porting aid. It is not recommended for new
projects, and existing projects that use it are advised to port away
from it, and use plain KParts instead.


%package devel
Summary:	Header files for %{kfname} development
Summary(pl.UTF-8):	Pliki nagłówkowe dla programistów używających %{kfname}
Group:		X11/Development/Libraries
Requires:	%{name} = %{version}-%{release}

%description devel
